latestPosts.caption:
Still waters run deep -  my next little show is soon opening in Paris,
bubbles with the mermaids, June 19 | 6–9 PM,  sink or swim ⛲️

Wet ontology - water, ripples, currents, dissolution, Venus emerging from blood + semen + sea foam, undersea volcanic explosions turning islands, stories of suicidal mermaids, Narcissus drowning in his own reflection, the mirrored world — as above so below — layers of reality: the surface, what floats upon it, what reflects within it, and what’s hidden in the unseen depths.
“The dream-world is the Aquarium of Night.” Apocalyptic rains, whirlpools, the world is aqueous, reality water-soluble. 🫧
 
(´Still waters run deep’ = ‘Méfiez vous de l’eau qui dort’)

-📸🪄 @latourfanny
